<h1 class="article">
  &quot;The Spandrels of San Marco and the Panglossian Paradigm: A Critique of the Adaptationist Programme&quot; (1979), by Stephen J. Gould and Richard C. Lewontin
</h1>
  
      
  </div>

  <div class="views-element-container block">

  
    

            <div>
<div class="authorsect view js-view-dom-id-5bf9970b7e5bb3f03fa1e02975b6283e6c1b3fb237aecac7480c71a47171ae72 view-keep-details">
       
        
        
        
            <div class="view-content">
        
    <div class="author">
          <span class="views-field views-field-field-contributor"><span class="field-content author-item">By: <strong>M. Elizabeth Barnes</strong></span></span>
      </div>

      </div>
      
        
        
        
        
        </div>
</div>

      
  </div>

